&lt;h2 id=&#34;异常处理&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#异常处理&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 异常处理&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;异常类&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#异常类&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 异常类&lt;/h3&gt;
